4\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43879,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/07\/03\/saeed-do-not-wish-evil\/","url_meta":{"origin":24156,"position":1},"title":"Sa\u2019id on Curses: Do not wish evil upon believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ata\u2019 ibn Dinar reported: Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cDo not supplicate for evil against the believing men and women, asking Allah to disgrace them and curse them and so on, for that is transgression in the saying of Allah Almighty: Call upon your Lord\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8217,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/prophet-described-tawrat-torah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24156,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawrat: The Prophet&#8217;s description in the Torah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ata' ibn Yasar reported: I met Abdullah ibn Amr, may Allah be pleased with him, and I said, \u201cTell me about the description of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, in the Torah.\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cBy Allah, he is described in the Torah with some of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43821,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/06\/29\/fudayl-ihsan-even-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":24156,"position":3},"title":"Fudayl on Ihsan: Be good to all creatures, even animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Thabit reported: Fudayl ibn \u2018Iyad, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnow that if the servant treated everyone well, but he was evil to his chickens, he would not be recorded among the good-doers.\u201d Source: Tafsi\u0304r Ibn Abi\u0304 H\u0323a\u0304tim 2:195 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062b\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u062a\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0641\u064f\u0636\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26866,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/11\/17\/shafii-desire-no-praise\/","url_meta":{"origin":24156,"position":4},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: I desire no praise or credit for teaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 17, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never debated anyone and loved for him to be wrong. There is no knowledge in my heart but that I wish everyone could have it and attribute none of it to me.\u201d Source: A\u0304da\u0304b al-Sha\u0304fi\u2019i\u0304 wa Mana\u0304qibuh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/10\/18\/umar-brings-tawrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24156,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Israiliyyat: Umar brings the Torah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 18, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: When Umar came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, he said, \u201cWe have heard wonderous stories from the Jews. Shall we write them down?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWill you fall into an abyss like the Jews and Christians? I have come to you\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24156","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=24156"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24156\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-js